{"tid":2087181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港市民對實施中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法(國安法)的聲明》","createTime":"2020-06-30T15:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:54:16.000Z","uid":177168,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7492a0abe481faa2428d6d24fc5ea04e49482a4f","tid":2087181,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"現宣佈700萬香港居民對《國安法》不予承認，中華人民共和國在過去23年對港非法行使主權，中英聯合聲明的制定亦違反《聯合國1514號決議》中之「住民自決」的原則。香港市民將公投決定是否脫離中華人民共和國<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2020年6月30日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間23時20分"},{"pid":"88f367f54731e176839b83658a3a7bd5a4590565","tid":2087181,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"希望樓豬係外國巴，如果唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港公安</span>好快mon到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1202041670e66839946f7012d18644e44bb881","tid":2087181,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"7.1"},{"pid":"810cc3f56b2ec69fd60483beda261ca3bea37abe","tid":2087181,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88f367f54731e176839b83658a3a7bd5a4590565","tid":2087181,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"希望樓豬係外國巴，如果唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港公安</span>好快mon到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3aea888a2d5cc3e148b45bbf35325ddebf2ad1","tid":2087181,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86876cda0e4ef440b38068a69317d76ddb0106b9","tid":2087181,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠟⠋⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⠄⢁⠈⢻⢿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿<br />\n⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠃⠄